WEBVTT

00:02:27.191 --> 00:02:31.494
Luana: We're just a tool for people
that want to send a positive message.

00:02:32.212 --> 00:02:34.340
Jamie: Step inside
and take a seat over here.

00:02:34.364 --> 00:02:36.398
Once the truck is ready and running,

00:02:36.422 --> 00:02:37.599
anyone can come.

00:02:40.550 --> 00:02:41.724
Wait for the flash.

00:02:42.058 --> 00:02:43.208
(Music)

00:02:44.166 --> 00:02:45.316
(Camera clicking)

00:02:47.525 --> 00:02:50.650
Touch the screen, take your picture,
type in information.

00:02:53.958 --> 00:02:55.775
In a matter of a minute or so,

00:02:56.506 --> 00:02:58.951
we print on the side, three by four feet.

00:02:59.474 --> 00:03:02.463
No one is used to seeing
their face so big.